        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is Yoast SEO?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yoast SEO is the most popular WordPress SEO plugin in the world, with 12M+ active installs. It provides real-time on-page SEO analysis via a green/orange/red traffic-light system, plus readability scoring, XML sitemaps, schema markup, and social previews. It does not create content or research keywords.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How much does Yoast SEO cost?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yoast SEO Free is $0. Premium is $99/year for a single site. Add-ons (WooCommerce, Local SEO, Video, News) are $69-$79/year each. The AI+ plan with brand monitoring is roughly $358/year. There's no monthly billing and a 30-day money-back guarantee.</div>
