        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Is Yoast SEO Premium worth it?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">For single-site owners who use the redirect manager and want internal-linking suggestions, yes — $99/year is fair. For multi-site owners and agencies, no. Rank Math's free version already includes 5 focus keywords, redirects, and local SEO that Yoast charges for.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Does Yoast SEO write content?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
