        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Is Yoast better than Rank Math?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">For WordPress beginners who want a clean, simple traffic-light interface — Yoast wins. For feature value and power users — Rank Math wins. Rank Math's free version includes 5 focus keywords, redirects, and local SEO. Yoast charges $99/year for those.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
